comment:
* Holder class to defer initializing sentinel objects only used
     * for serialization.

variables.name: STACK_TRACE_ELEMENT_SENTINEL
variables.comment:
* {@linkplain #setStackTrace(StackTraceElement[]) Setting the * stack trace} to a one-element array containing this sentinel * value indicates future attempts to set the stack trace will be * ignored. The sentinel is equal to the result of calling:
* {@code new StackTraceElement("", "", null, Integer.MIN_VALUE)}

variables.name: STACK_TRACE_SENTINEL
variables.comment:
* Sentinel value used in the serial form to indicate an immutable
         * stack trace.
